
 To build 
   UNIX> cd MEMPHYS/mgr
   UNIX> <in geant4_82 edit geant4_home to point to your geant4 installation>
   UNIX> <in run_setup[.sh,.csh] edit G4DATA env variable to point to the geant4 data>
   UNIX> ./build

 If having CERN-ROOT :
   UNIX> <in cern_root_setup[.sh,.csh] edit root_home to point to your CERN-ROOT installation>
     sh> . ./cern_root_setup.sh
   or from a csh flavoured shell :
    csh> source ./cern_root_setup.csh
   UNIX> ./build -root

 